  "detailed_description": "In a quiet medieval village, you suddenly receive a warning from your mentor:<br>Soon, everything here will be destroyed,<br>To change the language of this disaster,<br>You pick up the weapon in hand, solemn and stirring forward...<br><br><br>Game system Overview:<br>* It's a RogueLike gameplay combined with action adventure<br>* A rich variety of attack moves that can be used alternately in battle to defeat different combinations of enemies.<br>* Multiple layers of defense to block and counter the enemy.<br>* Different effects of equipment appear randomly, enrich your fantasy adventure.<br>* Increase your character's strange abilities by learning skills.<br>* Lots of weapon skills and special effects<br>* Random events lead to choices, and each choice will determine your future path.<br><br>* It's a RogueLike gameplay combined with action adventure<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/f51663891692ab956be223ed6782cb0b.poster.avif?t=1748611657\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/f51663891692ab956be223ed6782cb0b.webm?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/f51663891692ab956be223ed6782cb0b.mp4?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* A rich variety of attack moves that can be used alternately in battle to defeat different combinations of enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/bcbe25a7353a19495891695993fb6265.poster.avif?t=1748611657\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/bcbe25a7353a19495891695993fb6265.webm?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/bcbe25a7353a19495891695993fb6265.mp4?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* Increase your character's strange abilities by learning skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/c672e2e97188892967dcfc9d89fc26fb.poster.avif?t=1748611657\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/c672e2e97188892967dcfc9d89fc26fb.webm?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/c672e2e97188892967dcfc9d89fc26fb.mp4?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* Lots of weapon skills and special effects<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/92091ac485d6fe24d2a19edf95025939.poster.avif?t=1748611657\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/92091ac485d6fe24d2a19edf95025939.webm?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/92091ac485d6fe24d2a19edf95025939.mp4?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* Random events lead to choices, and each choice will determine your future path.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/27b811957bf02f88dba8bc95b0dde240.poster.avif?t=1748611657\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://s