  "about_the_game": "In a quiet medieval village, you suddenly receive a warning from your mentor:<br>Soon, everything here will be destroyed,<br>To change the language of this disaster,<br>You pick up the weapon in hand, solemn and stirring forward...<br><br><br>Game system Overview:<br>* It's a RogueLike gameplay combined with action adventure<br>* A rich variety of attack moves that can be used alternately in battle to defeat different combinations of enemies.<br>* Multiple layers of defense to block and counter the enemy.<br>* Different effects of equipment appear randomly, enrich your fantasy adventure.<br>* Increase your character's strange abilities by learning skills.<br>* Lots of weapon skills and special effects<br>* Random events lead to choices, and each choice will determine your future path.<br><br>* It's a RogueLike gameplay combined with action adventure<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/f51663891692ab956be223ed6782cb0b.poster.avif?t=1748611657\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/f51663891692ab956be223ed6782cb0b.webm?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/f51663891692ab956be223ed6782cb0b.mp4?t=1748611657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* A rich variety of attack moves that can be used alternately in battle to defeat different combinations of enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/bcbe25a7353a19495891695993fb6265.poster.avif?t=1748611657\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1690180/extras/bcbe25a7353a194